<section class="skills" id="skills">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">// Skills & Profile</h2>
    
    <div class="profile-grid">
      <div class="profile-card">
        <h3>$ whoami</h3>
        <p>Técnico en sistemas con habilidades en creación, reparación y mantenimiento de hardware y software. Experiencia práctica en desarrollo web y configuración de equipos de red (switches/routers) mediante SSH. Habilidades blandas desarrolladas como monitor académico.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="profile-card">
        <h3>$ cat objective.txt</h3>
        <p>Desarrollar, mantener y dar soporte de software, red de internet o hardware para una empresa o cliente.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="skills-grid">
      <div class="skill-category">
        <h3><span class="prompt">$</span> Web Development</h3>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="skill-tag">React</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">JavaScript</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">CSS</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">HTML</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-category">
        <h3><span class="prompt">$</span> Programming</h3>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="skill-tag">Java</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Python</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-category">
        <h3><span class="prompt">$</span> Networking</h3>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="skill-tag">Cisco (L2/L3)</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">IPv4/IPv6</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">VLAN</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">DHCP</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">NAT</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-category">
        <h3><span class="prompt">$</span> Systems & Tools</h3>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="skill-tag">Linux</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Windows</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">VirtualBox</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Figma</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Packet Tracer</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-category">
        <h3><span class="prompt">$</span> Security</h3>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="skill-tag">Firewalls</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Vulnerability Analysis</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Best Practices</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-category">
        <h3><span class="prompt">$</span> Hardware</h3>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="skill-tag">Assembly</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Repair</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Diagnostics</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .skills {
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .profile-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .profile-card {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-matrix-primary);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .profile-card:hover {
    background: rgba(0, 55, 20, 0.1);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.2);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .profile-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-matrix);
    color: var(--color-matrix-primary);
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .profile-card p {
    color: #ddd;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .skills-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .skill-category {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-matrix-primary);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.2);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .skill-category:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.4);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .skill-category h3 {
    font-family: 'VT323', monospace;
    color: #fff;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    background: rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.1);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-matrix-primary);
    border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
  }

  .skill-tags {
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .prompt {
    color: var(--color-matrix-accent);
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
  }

  .skill-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .skill-tag {
    background: rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-matrix-primary);
    color: var(--color-matrix-primary);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .skill-tag:hover {
    background: rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.2);
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.3);
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .skills {
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
